<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2026-06-16T09:52:35-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Mountain in the Sand</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260616/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Mountain in the Sand" /><published>2026-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-16T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sand-mountain</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260616/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Marks on the sand at low tide, like a sumi-e ink painting.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">砂の中の山</span>
干潮時の砂に刻まれた跡は、まるで墨絵のようだ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Dawn" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Marks on the sand at low tide, like a sumi-e ink painting. 砂の中の山 干潮時の砂に刻まれた跡は、まるで墨絵のようだ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02348_edit-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02348_edit-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">SoCal Suburbia</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260615/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="SoCal Suburbia" /><published>2026-06-15T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-15T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/suburbia</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260615/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The colorful uniformity of a Southern California planned community. Blue skies and the soft light of the fog rolling in.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">南カリフォルニアの郊外</span>
南カリフォルニアの計画都市が醸し出す、色彩豊かな均一感。青い空と、流れ込む霧の柔らかな光。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The colorful uniformity of a Southern California planned community. Blue skies and the soft light of the fog rolling in. 南カリフォルニアの郊外 南カリフォルニアの計画都市が醸し出す、色彩豊かな均一感。青い空と、流れ込む霧の柔らかな光。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02308_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02308_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">King Harbor</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260614/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="King Harbor" /><published>2026-06-14T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-14T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/king-harbor</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260614/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The setting sun reflects in the water, at the entrance to King Harbor in Redondo Beach.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">キング・ハーバー</span>
レドンド・ビーチのキング・ハーバーの入り口で、夕日が水面に映る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Harbors" /><category term="King Harbor" /><category term="Piers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The setting sun reflects in the water, at the entrance to King Harbor in Redondo Beach. キング・ハーバー レドンド・ビーチのキング・ハーバーの入り口で、夕日が水面に映る。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02280-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02280-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">The Next LACMA</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260612/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="The Next LACMA" /><published>2026-06-12T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-12T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/wilshire</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260612/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Standing over Wilshire Blvd. in the new LA County Museum of Art. The street, newly reconstructed, looks like a perfect LEGO reproduction. The subway being built underneath Wilshire Blvd. opened last month.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">新生LACMA</span>
新しいロサンゼルス・カウンティ美術館からウィルシャー大通りを見下ろす。新しく再整備された通りは、まるでレゴで完璧に再現されたかのようだ。ウィルシャー大通りの地下で建設中だった地下鉄は、先月開通した。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Los Angeles" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Standing over Wilshire Blvd. in the new LA County Museum of Art. The street, newly reconstructed, looks like a perfect LEGO reproduction. The subway being built underneath Wilshire Blvd. opened last month. 新生LACMA 新しいロサンゼルス・カウンティ美術館からウィルシャー大通りを見下ろす。新しく再整備された通りは、まるでレゴで完璧に再現されたかのようだ。ウィルシャー大通りの地下で建設中だった地下鉄は、先月開通した。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2634.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2634.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Vista Point</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260610/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Vista Point" /><published>2026-06-10T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-10T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/vista-point</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260610/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Sunset from the cliffs of the Palos Verdes Peninsula, in the southern part of Los Angeles County.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ヴィスタ・ポイント</span>
ロサンゼルス郡南部のパロス・ベルデス半島の崖から望む夕日。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Sunset from the cliffs of the Palos Verdes Peninsula, in the southern part of Los Angeles County. ヴィスタ・ポイント ロサンゼルス郡南部のパロス・ベルデス半島の崖から望む夕日。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02210-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02210-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">South Bay View</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260609/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="South Bay View" /><published>2026-06-09T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-09T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/south-bay</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260609/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking north from Hermosa Beach at the Manhattan Beach Pier and El Segundo, a view I've photographed many times before. Gentle waves break on the shore.
</p>
<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">サウス・ベイの眺め</span>
ハーモサ・ビーチから北を望むマンハッタン・ビーチ・ピアとエル・セグンドの景色。これまでに何度も撮影してきた場所だ。穏やかな波が岸に打ち寄せる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking north from Hermosa Beach at the Manhattan Beach Pier and El Segundo, a view I've photographed many times before. Gentle waves break on the shore. サウス・ベイの眺め ハーモサ・ビーチから北を望むマンハッタン・ビーチ・ピアとエル・セグンドの景色。これまでに何度も撮影してきた場所だ。穏やかな波が岸に打ち寄せる。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02143_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02143_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">A Hermosa Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260608/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="A Hermosa Sunset" /><published>2026-06-08T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-08T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260608/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The summer sun sets over Malibu, at the opposite end of the Santa Monica Bay.
</p>
