</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Southern California" /><category term="Aerial" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Flying over the Santa Monica mountain range in Malibu. The white at the top of the frame are clouds covering the ocean. サンタモニカ山脈 マリブのサンタモニカ山脈の上空を飛んでいる。画面上部の白い部分は、海を覆う雲だ。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2568_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_IMG_2568_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Freeway Aerial</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260605/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Freeway Aerial" /><published>2026-06-05T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2026-06-05T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/freeway</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260605/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
