</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The Ryotei tea house and Hydrangea in bloom along the Dai-Sensui pond at Kiyosumi Garden. 清澄庭園の大泉池沿いに、料亭と咲き誇るアジサイが見られる。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02111.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2606_A7R02111.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>